description:
A UK based artist Gavin. Published by Image Comics in their 2011 Thought Bubble Anthology.

In October 2012 he completed Garbage Boy comic book with writer Anthony Rella and November 2012 saw him complete the illustration for the poster for the Hollywood movie Halfway To A Blackout.

He has recently published a 50 page revamping of the UK's first comic book supernatural sleuth Dene Vernon, Man Of Mystery with writer Terry Hooper entitled 'The Thing From Below'. Also just finished is a second Chung Ling Soo comic book entitled 'The Case Of The Thames Serpent' which is also available from Black Tower Comics. He also writes and edits publishes the Marc Bolan Magazine called 'A Thousand Mark Feld Charms' which has been published since 1996.
name: Gavin Ross
